{"tid":910828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收押所賣食物被冚引發66犯搞對抗　懲教飛虎鎮壓","createTime":"2018-11-21T12:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:31:45.000Z","uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb148187ebf5962491bc86eef910221a25476a88","tid":910828,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121163330518-1121_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181121190702\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121163330518-1121_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181121190702&h=414a6d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荔枝角收押所爆出「監獄風雲」。懲教署表示，該收押所管方近月採取連串措施打擊院所內還押在囚人士的非法食物買賣活動，今早(21日)約8時紀律檢控2名男囚犯藏有非法物品。管方及後接獲情報，指部分在囚人士計劃集體行動對抗管方。 <br />\n<br />\n今早約10時30分，66名男還押犯人集體投訴，要求管方取消對上述男囚犯的紀律檢控。經評估及部署後，署方於下午2時增派人手及調動資源增援，當中包括有懲教「飛虎隊」之稱的區域應變隊、支援隊伍及警衞犬隊，對目標地點及人物進行突擊搜查。 <br />\n<br />\n現時，共有5名還押犯人懷疑煽動其他犯人進行集體非法活動，正被隔離及接受調查，署方會繼續密切監察有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121163330518-1121_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181121190702\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121163330518-1121_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181121190702&h=1954c469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1578b6db5dd5828d051019bcc309b552ace372c2","tid":910828,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://datalib.ent.qq.com/movie/pic/lib/2006-09-22/2006092216530914444624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdatalib.ent.qq.com%2Fmovie%2Fpic%2Flib%2F2006-09-22%2F2006092216530914444624.jpg&h=b0dcb1c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7445e3b71f68be13a6c8dbfbe94f4d87b96624fe","tid":910828,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}